<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5181893>
    dc:description "Figure 2. (a) A urohyal with ventral apex about equidistant between rostral and caudal tips (Astyanax mexicanus, UMMZ 169835); (b) closer to caudal end (A. tehuacanensis sp. nov., UMMZ 198853)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5181893/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5181969>
    dc:description "Figure 47. Astyanax tehuacanensis sp. nov., holotype, UMMZ 250295." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5181969/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5181913>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Map of Mexico, showing distribution localities of Astyanax acatlanensis sp. nov., A. argentatus, A. mexicanus, A. rioverde sp. nov., A. salvatoris sp. nov., A. tamiahua sp. nov. and A. tehuacanensis sp. nov. A larger symbol denotes the type locality (ambiguous for A. mexicanus; see text)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5181913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

